      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a dependable choice for its next owner. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, with all major systems functioning properly. While there are some minor cosmetic blemishes consistent with careful use\u2014such as light surface scratches and small interior wear spots\u2014the car remains very presentable and mechanically sound. It\u2019s a great value for someone looking for a high-quality, reliable vehicle without the premium price of a showroom-new model.",
